WEBVTT

01:42.320 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:52.320 --> 01:53.320
Sang Zhi.

01:56.680 --> 01:58.760
Can you come with me to buy something?

02:10.680 --> 02:11.520
So?

02:11.600 --> 02:14.200
Grade 11, Class 1's classroom is empty.

02:14.280 --> 02:15.200
Empty?

02:15.880 --> 02:17.000
Yes.

02:17.080 --> 02:18.280
Can I search inside?

02:18.920 --> 02:20.360
The classes are over.

02:20.440 --> 02:21.640
There are no students left.

02:22.680 --> 02:23.560
Okay.

02:24.080 --> 02:27.360
If you see her later,

02:27.440 --> 02:29.200
can you tell her to wait here?

02:29.280 --> 02:30.720
- Sure.
- Thank you.

02:30.800 --> 02:31.720
You're welcome.

02:36.200 --> 02:41.840
XIANGJUAN NOODLES

02:41.920 --> 02:42.880
Wait, Zhenru.

02:43.600 --> 02:45.840
The stationery shop is that way.

02:46.440 --> 02:48.200
I want to visit the one by the alley.

02:50.040 --> 02:50.920
Okay.

02:58.880 --> 03:00.360
We have to hurry up.

03:00.440 --> 03:02.680
I don't want to keep my brother waiting.

03:05.920 --> 03:06.760
Zhenru.

03:07.280 --> 03:08.840
Is something bothering you?

03:08.920 --> 03:10.240
What happened?

03:10.840 --> 03:11.760
Nothing.

03:12.640 --> 03:13.560
Nothing?

03:14.920 --> 03:17.320
Sang Zhi, do you have money with you?

03:19.440 --> 03:20.400
Good.

03:21.040 --> 03:22.600
I was afraid I didn't bring enough.

03:23.160 --> 03:24.640
We should have enough.

03:24.720 --> 03:27.520
I did bring an extra 50 yuan today.

03:28.200 --> 03:29.560
What do you want to buy?

03:29.640 --> 03:31.080
How much does it cost?

03:31.160 --> 03:32.320
Sang Zhi.

03:32.400 --> 03:33.880
Let's go over there.

03:42.680 --> 03:43.840
Over there? Why?

03:46.680 --> 03:47.560
I want

03:48.400 --> 03:49.920
to visit the cybercafe.

03:53.400 --> 03:55.640
But our teacher told us not to go there

03:55.720 --> 03:57.000
because it's dangerous.

03:57.600 --> 03:58.480
Let's not go there.

03:58.560 --> 04:01.280
Just go with me this once, please?

04:01.360 --> 04:02.640
I promise I won't go there again.

04:03.200 --> 04:04.160
Just come with me.

04:05.280 --> 04:07.120
Zhenru, we shouldn't go there.

04:07.200 --> 04:09.280
Let's go to the stationery shop.

04:09.360 --> 04:10.280
Come.

04:13.400 --> 04:14.280
Never mind.

04:15.240 --> 04:16.519
I'll go there by myself.

04:16.600 --> 04:17.480
Zhenru!

04:18.399 --> 04:19.519
Zhenru!

04:25.040 --> 04:26.440
Zhenru, wait for me!

04:26.520 --> 04:27.840
Don't go there alone!

04:29.040 --> 04:29.960
Zhenru!

04:57.120 --> 04:57.960
Sir.

04:58.040 --> 05:00.680
Have you seen a female high school student

05:00.760 --> 05:02.160
with an injured leg passing by here?

05:02.800 --> 05:04.400
I think she went into the alley up ahead

05:04.480 --> 05:05.680
with another student.

05:06.360 --> 05:07.480
The alley up ahead?

05:08.400 --> 05:09.240
Thank you.

05:09.720 --> 05:11.520
What took you so long?

05:11.600 --> 05:12.880
We've been waiting a long time.

05:13.560 --> 05:15.640
My teacher kept us late.

05:16.720 --> 05:17.840
Really?

05:17.920 --> 05:19.440
I thought you fled.

05:19.920 --> 05:21.040
And we were thinking

05:21.120 --> 05:22.720
we would visit you at school tomorrow.

05:23.720 --> 05:25.040
I don't have money.

05:25.120 --> 05:26.880
My parents didn't give me any.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.480
No money?

05:28.560 --> 05:30.000
Remember what you said yesterday?

05:30.080 --> 05:32.000
My friend here has some.

05:36.360 --> 05:37.920
How much?

05:47.240 --> 05:48.280
Is this all you have?

05:48.360 --> 05:50.360
Do you have to be so broke?

05:51.000 --> 05:52.520
And crippled at that.

05:52.600 --> 05:54.400
Come. Frisk her.

05:57.240 --> 05:58.640
She has nothing.

06:04.680 --> 06:05.920
You have no money,

06:06.000 --> 06:07.440
but your parents must have some.

06:08.320 --> 06:09.520
Tomorrow, after school,

06:09.600 --> 06:11.360
meet me here with the money.

06:11.440 --> 06:13.040
Did I make myself clear, cripple?

06:14.320 --> 06:15.480
You too.

06:15.560 --> 06:16.560
Understood?

06:16.640 --> 06:17.520
Yes.

06:18.520 --> 06:19.520
That's a good girl.

06:20.880 --> 06:22.400
See you tomorrow.

06:24.080 --> 06:24.920
Let's go.

06:28.320 --> 06:30.600
Gosh. What are we now? Beggars?

06:46.880 --> 06:47.760
Do you know them?

06:48.880 --> 06:49.920
I don't.

06:50.520 --> 06:52.400
I met them in the cybercafe yesterday.

07:01.120 --> 07:03.240
Sang Zhi, I'm sorry.

07:04.640 --> 07:06.840
I have no more money

07:07.320 --> 07:08.960
and my parents wouldn't give me more.

07:11.280 --> 07:12.840
I had no other choice.

07:12.920 --> 07:14.400
Sorry, Sang Zhi. Don't be mad at me.

07:14.480 --> 07:15.720
They just want money.

07:15.800 --> 07:17.440
They won't do anything to us.

07:17.520 --> 07:19.160
Besides, the school break is coming up.

07:19.240 --> 07:21.040
They'll move on once the break starts.

07:22.760 --> 07:23.600
Sang Zhi.

07:25.160 --> 07:26.520
You ignored me

07:26.600 --> 07:27.760
after Fu Zhengchu's birthday.

07:29.600 --> 07:30.800
You didn't care

07:32.080 --> 07:33.640
when I fell on Sports Day.

07:35.840 --> 07:36.960
And I was wondering

07:38.680 --> 07:40.320
why you suddenly talked to me today.

07:48.240 --> 07:49.560
When you get home,

07:49.640 --> 07:51.680
tell your parents everything.

07:52.480 --> 07:53.920
Just tell them the truth.

07:55.520 --> 07:57.000
Tell them to inform the school.

07:57.080 --> 07:58.520
Don't listen to the bullies.

07:58.600 --> 08:00.120
They're just trying to intimidate you.

08:01.040 --> 08:03.240
Your parents will help you, won't they?

08:11.000 --> 08:11.960
Go home now.

08:14.800 --> 08:16.160
Bye.

08:17.720 --> 08:19.560
Sang Zhi, I'm sorry.

08:20.120 --> 08:21.160
Sang Zhi.

08:21.800 --> 08:23.440
- Sang Zhi, sorry.
- Don't follow me!

08:56.800 --> 08:57.920
Sang Zhi!

09:09.040 --> 09:10.080
Where were you?

09:10.800 --> 09:12.080
Why didn't you answer your phone?

09:14.840 --> 09:16.400
Didn't Sang Yan tell you to wait for me?

09:19.920 --> 09:20.880
What's wrong?

09:41.520 --> 09:42.720
It's okay.

09:42.800 --> 09:43.800
I'm here.

09:59.840 --> 10:01.840
CHAPTER FOUR, HIDDEN APPROVAL

10:01.920 --> 10:03.480
MY SECRET

10:05.320 --> 10:06.440
Thank you.

10:12.520 --> 10:13.440
Drink something.

10:15.440 --> 10:17.080
- Thank you, Jiaxu.
- Don't mention it.

10:19.440 --> 10:20.520
What happened to your hand?

10:24.400 --> 10:25.880
Did someone bully you?

10:34.000 --> 10:35.200
Why didn't you tell me?

10:36.920 --> 10:38.960
I don't want to cause you trouble.

10:39.040 --> 10:40.720
Sang Yan also told me

10:40.800 --> 10:42.120
that you are very busy,

10:42.200 --> 10:43.440
so I shouldn't bother you.

10:45.320 --> 10:47.120
But don't worry, Jiaxu.

10:47.200 --> 10:48.880
I won't hide this from anyone.

10:48.960 --> 10:51.280
I'll tell my parents when I get home.

10:51.360 --> 10:52.320
Don't worry.

10:53.160 --> 10:54.280
Where did they hit you?

10:56.480 --> 10:57.680
They didn't hit me.

10:57.760 --> 10:59.760
Didn't they? Look at your hand.

11:02.080 --> 11:04.200
They only tapped my cheek

11:04.680 --> 11:07.000
and took my wallet.

11:07.600 --> 11:09.240
I hurt my hand on my own.

11:09.320 --> 11:11.360
They told me

11:11.880 --> 11:14.880
to come to them with the money tomorrow.

11:23.080 --> 11:24.000
Jiaxu.

11:24.080 --> 11:25.320
I'll be fine.

11:25.400 --> 11:26.480
Don't worry.

11:28.000 --> 11:29.360
Why would you go to a back alley?

11:31.920 --> 11:33.960
A friend brought me there.

11:34.040 --> 11:34.920
Who?

11:37.720 --> 11:39.040
She was being extorted too.

11:39.680 --> 11:41.200
She was scared,

11:41.280 --> 11:42.800
so she brought me with her.

11:42.880 --> 11:44.680
Instead of telling her teacher or parents

11:44.760 --> 11:45.840
about the extortion,

11:45.920 --> 11:47.160
why did she bring you with her?

11:48.440 --> 11:49.720
She was worried

11:49.800 --> 11:51.760
that those bullies would take revenge

11:51.840 --> 11:53.680
if she told on them.

11:57.680 --> 12:00.960
You don't need a friend like that.

12:05.200 --> 12:06.320
Also,

12:07.000 --> 12:08.560
always tell your parents

12:09.040 --> 12:10.440
when something happens.

12:11.120 --> 12:12.840
They will always protect you.

12:12.920 --> 12:13.880
Understood?

12:35.400 --> 12:36.520
How do you go home

12:37.080 --> 12:38.960
when Sang Yan picks you up from school?

12:43.880 --> 12:45.640
We take a bus.

12:45.720 --> 12:46.600
A bus?

12:47.880 --> 12:50.480
What if someone steps on your foot
on the bus?

12:59.880 --> 13:00.840
Give me a moment.

13:08.800 --> 13:09.760
Okay.

13:12.560 --> 13:14.200
Okay, come on.

13:14.280 --> 13:15.600
Where are we going?

13:15.680 --> 13:16.560
I'm seeing you home.

13:31.200 --> 13:32.240
Come.

13:37.880 --> 13:38.720
Get on.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.320
Sit tight.

14:00.280 --> 14:01.320
Hold on tight.

14:01.400 --> 14:02.440
Don't have another fall.

14:04.920 --> 14:07.160
Have you taken this route home before?

14:09.240 --> 14:10.080
No.

14:10.160 --> 14:11.640
Isn't the scenery nice?

14:19.240 --> 14:20.080
Jiaxu.

14:21.160 --> 14:22.360
Where is Sang Yan?

14:23.720 --> 14:26.280
I think he went to an interview.

14:27.200 --> 14:28.080
An interview?

14:28.160 --> 14:29.240
For a part-time job?

14:30.920 --> 14:32.120
No.

14:32.800 --> 14:34.680
Graduation is coming up,

14:34.760 --> 14:36.320
so everyone is looking for jobs.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.360
Are you going back to Yihe

14:39.000 --> 14:40.720
to work?

14:45.480 --> 14:46.720
I haven't decided yet.

14:49.520 --> 14:50.800
I quite like Nanwu too.

14:59.240 --> 15:00.280
Do you feel better now?

15:03.520 --> 15:05.160
You're in 11th grade now.

15:05.240 --> 15:06.840
You will face more and more stress,

15:07.880 --> 15:09.720
so you need to find a way

15:09.800 --> 15:11.280
to decompress.

15:12.040 --> 15:13.320
For example, cycling.

15:57.520 --> 15:59.240
If you're ever overwhelmed by studying,

15:59.320 --> 16:00.760
don't keep it bottled up.

16:00.840 --> 16:02.360
Tell Sang Yan or me.

16:02.920 --> 16:04.000
We have been through this.

16:05.320 --> 16:07.760
I'll be grateful
if he doesn't make fun of me.

16:08.560 --> 16:10.160
The next time he makes fun of you,

16:10.240 --> 16:11.080
let me know.

16:16.800 --> 16:18.080
Here.

16:23.960 --> 16:25.320
Take this.

16:27.520 --> 16:30.400
Tell your parents what happened today.

16:39.760 --> 16:41.120
Take it.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.320
Go home now.

16:55.520 --> 16:56.840
Bye, Jiaxu.

16:57.400 --> 16:58.240
Bye.

19:37.480 --> 19:39.040
I have a secret.

19:42.400 --> 19:45.400
I don't want to admit it,

19:48.800 --> 19:49.760
but

19:56.280 --> 19:57.440
I seem

20:02.360 --> 20:04.120
to have fallen for him.

20:09.400 --> 20:13.520
Duan Jiaxu.

20:18.800 --> 20:20.120
I HAVE A SECRET

21:15.400 --> 21:17.640
OCTOBER 27TH, TUESDAY

21:17.720 --> 21:22.600
I SEEM TO HAVE FALLEN FOR YOU

21:24.080 --> 21:25.240
He's so handsome.

21:41.000 --> 21:42.240
Little demon!

21:43.520 --> 21:44.360
Come back.

21:45.200 --> 21:46.160
I'm here.

21:49.560 --> 21:50.480
Come!

21:58.240 --> 21:59.440
Tell me.

21:59.520 --> 22:01.640
Did those extorters tell you
to meet them today?

22:03.080 --> 22:04.120
We don't have to do that.

22:04.200 --> 22:05.320
Lead the way.

22:05.400 --> 22:07.720
- We really don't have to.
- Lead the way!

22:07.800 --> 22:08.760
Listen up.

22:08.840 --> 22:10.400
They messed with the wrong people.

22:10.480 --> 22:12.160
Go. Lead the way.

22:12.240 --> 22:13.600
Don't worry. We're here.

22:13.680 --> 22:15.040
We'll teach them a lesson.

22:23.080 --> 22:24.320
Come on. This way.

22:26.880 --> 22:28.200
It's not embarrassing at all.

22:36.200 --> 22:37.040
We're here.

22:38.640 --> 22:39.520
Is it here?

22:43.120 --> 22:44.600
Stay here, little demon.

22:46.040 --> 22:47.640
Describe their appearance to me.

22:49.720 --> 22:50.680
One of them

22:51.760 --> 22:52.920
has dyed hair.

22:53.440 --> 22:54.320
Another one

22:55.000 --> 22:56.280
has short hair.

22:56.360 --> 22:58.280
One has long hair.

22:58.360 --> 22:59.360
They are

23:01.320 --> 23:03.440
three girls about this tall.

23:04.040 --> 23:05.280
One is shorter.

23:08.760 --> 23:11.200
Why didn't you tell us they are girls?

23:11.280 --> 23:12.400
You didn't ask.

23:12.480 --> 23:13.960
I told you not to do this.

23:14.040 --> 23:16.000
I can't do this against girls.

23:16.640 --> 23:17.520
Let's head back.

23:18.280 --> 23:19.160
No way.

23:19.240 --> 23:20.240
Girls or boys,

23:20.320 --> 23:21.680
they can't bully my sister.

23:22.640 --> 23:25.000
But four boys going against three girls

23:25.080 --> 23:25.920
doesn't sound right.

23:26.000 --> 23:26.920
Yes.

23:27.680 --> 23:29.040
How about this?

23:29.120 --> 23:30.120
Do you want out?

23:31.920 --> 23:33.120
Stay here with her.

23:33.200 --> 23:35.560
You and you, come.

23:35.640 --> 23:36.600
Let's go!

23:36.680 --> 23:37.760
Wait for me, Sang Zhi.

23:39.960 --> 23:41.120
- Hold this for me.
- Okay.

23:42.080 --> 23:42.920
Don't worry.

23:48.800 --> 23:50.920
Junwen, will they get into a fight?

23:52.280 --> 23:54.080
Maybe, if the bullies are boys.

23:54.160 --> 23:56.120
But you said they are girls.

23:56.200 --> 23:57.680
They will probably just talk to them.

24:04.120 --> 24:05.480
Help me open it.

24:06.280 --> 24:07.120
Okay.

24:08.720 --> 24:09.760
Does your wound still hurt?

24:19.600 --> 24:22.600
Did you hear that girl just now?

24:22.680 --> 24:24.160
- She's so meek.
- That cripple.

24:34.640 --> 24:35.520
Who are you?

24:36.920 --> 24:38.360
Wait.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.440
What are you doing?

24:39.520 --> 24:41.360
Smoking at such a young age?

24:41.440 --> 24:42.680
What are you doing?

24:42.760 --> 24:43.800
I heard

24:44.920 --> 24:47.200
that you extorted money from my friend.

24:49.120 --> 24:50.120
I don't know you guys.

24:50.200 --> 24:51.320
Who are you?

24:51.400 --> 24:53.160
It doesn't matter.
I know you, that's enough.

24:54.520 --> 24:56.200
You extorted 50 yuan from my sister

24:56.680 --> 24:58.720
and even slapped and threatened her.

25:00.600 --> 25:01.600
I didn't threaten her.

25:01.680 --> 25:03.240
I only took 50 yuan from her.

25:03.320 --> 25:04.360
I didn't do anything else.

25:04.440 --> 25:05.560
Don't make things up.

25:12.320 --> 25:13.400
I…

25:13.480 --> 25:15.080
I only took 50 yuan from her.

25:15.800 --> 25:16.960
I can give it back.

25:17.040 --> 25:19.080
I must settle this score with you

25:19.160 --> 25:22.480
even if you only took two yuan
from my sister.

25:23.240 --> 25:24.120
Give me the wallet.

25:26.520 --> 25:27.560
Hurry up!

25:34.320 --> 25:35.760
How old are you?

25:35.840 --> 25:37.640
Why are you hustling in the street

25:37.720 --> 25:38.640
instead of studying?

25:39.320 --> 25:40.360
You got the money.

25:40.440 --> 25:41.960
Mind your own business and leave.

25:42.760 --> 25:43.920
We got the money.

25:44.000 --> 25:45.040
But there's one more thing.

25:45.840 --> 25:46.680
Which of you

25:47.360 --> 25:48.720
is the leader?

25:55.720 --> 25:56.640
Is it you?

25:58.480 --> 25:59.840
Are you scared now?

26:05.560 --> 26:06.560
Little girl.

26:07.440 --> 26:09.640
Violence cannot solve anything.

26:10.600 --> 26:12.760
Only the weak

26:12.840 --> 26:14.280
bully those weaker than them.

26:15.400 --> 26:16.440
Do you hear me?

26:24.080 --> 26:25.720
Focus on your studies

26:25.800 --> 26:27.200
and don't do this again.

26:27.280 --> 26:28.160
Let's go.

27:05.640 --> 27:06.800
How did you settle it?

27:06.880 --> 27:08.880
By scaring them? Tell me. I'm curious.

27:08.960 --> 27:10.720
Listen, this is what I told them.

27:11.280 --> 27:13.000
I kill ten people every month

27:13.080 --> 27:14.400
and I've hit my quota this month.

27:14.480 --> 27:16.080
I'll return next month to kill them.

27:16.160 --> 27:17.440
Come on. Don't bluff.

27:17.520 --> 27:19.640
- I--
- Yes, I'm messing with you.

27:19.720 --> 27:20.600
Fine.

27:21.560 --> 27:22.840
Kiddo.

27:22.920 --> 27:24.920
The way you eat makes you
look like a pufferfish.

27:26.800 --> 27:28.000
You're the pufferfish.

27:28.840 --> 27:29.760
Really?

27:29.840 --> 27:30.960
Give me a lollipop then.

27:31.040 --> 27:33.040
I'll show you a handsome pufferfish.

27:34.240 --> 27:35.160
Please.

27:35.760 --> 27:37.040
Have mine.

27:37.120 --> 27:38.360
Don't tease her. Here.

27:38.440 --> 27:39.640
Save it for yourself.

27:39.720 --> 27:40.800
You can have it.

27:41.360 --> 27:42.200
What? No.

27:42.760 --> 27:43.840
I don't want it.

27:43.920 --> 27:44.840
I have had it before.

27:46.720 --> 27:47.760
Jiaxu.

27:52.520 --> 27:53.480
Get yourself some candy.

27:58.680 --> 28:00.640
I was joking.

28:00.720 --> 28:02.240
Keep it. Buy candy for yourself.

28:05.240 --> 28:06.440
Think of it

28:08.280 --> 28:09.520
as returning your 20 yuan.

28:13.720 --> 28:14.600
Okay.

28:16.000 --> 28:17.520
Then…

28:17.600 --> 28:19.520
Thank you for giving me spending money.

28:24.720 --> 28:25.600
Let's go.

28:29.640 --> 28:30.480
What are you doing?

28:31.800 --> 28:32.680
What do you mean?

28:33.680 --> 28:35.080
You're so annoying.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.280
Who said you could have it?

28:37.960 --> 28:39.320
Hey!

28:40.240 --> 28:41.440
Give it back.

28:41.520 --> 28:43.440
I already sucked on it.

28:43.520 --> 28:45.080
Do you still want it?

28:46.160 --> 28:47.160
Hey, give it back.

28:47.800 --> 28:48.640
Give it back!

28:48.720 --> 28:50.040
I still have one here.

28:50.120 --> 28:51.880
Wait. Give it back!

28:51.960 --> 28:53.240
Why do I get the feeling

28:53.320 --> 28:54.880
that she seems more like Jiaxu's sister?

28:54.960 --> 28:56.400
You can be his sister too.

28:57.200 --> 28:58.600
Come on. Let's go eat.

29:02.000 --> 29:03.560
NOVEMBER 11TH, WEDNESDAY

29:03.640 --> 29:09.920
SANG YAN SAID THAT
JIAXU SEEMS MORE LIKE MY BROTHER

29:12.560 --> 29:16.360
If only he really was my brother.

29:21.240 --> 29:23.160
He is the warmest person I know.

29:25.040 --> 29:27.400
In moments of need,

29:27.480 --> 29:29.760
he always gives me care and strength.

29:45.240 --> 29:46.720
I want to grow up faster

29:47.520 --> 29:48.840
and become a better person.

29:50.520 --> 29:51.920
I want to be just like him,

29:52.680 --> 29:54.440
someone who gives warmth to others.

31:59.680 --> 32:01.280
Yin Zhenru

32:01.360 --> 32:03.520
is transferring schools
for personal reasons.

32:04.480 --> 32:06.760
She will not come to class anymore.

32:15.240 --> 32:17.880
Sorry for the trouble, sir.

32:19.200 --> 32:20.160
Let's go.

32:21.880 --> 32:23.280
Do you see what you've done?

32:41.040 --> 32:42.720
Many students have fallen victim

32:42.800 --> 32:44.360
to extortion and blackmailing

32:44.440 --> 32:45.760
in nearby areas lately.

32:46.800 --> 32:48.760
The school takes this seriously.

32:49.840 --> 32:51.120
The bullies

32:51.200 --> 32:53.040
have been given disciplinary measures.

32:53.120 --> 32:55.200
The police have also lectured them.

32:56.040 --> 32:57.320
If you find yourself

32:57.400 --> 32:58.680
in a similar situation,

32:58.760 --> 33:01.760
you must notify the teachers
and your parents right away.

33:01.840 --> 33:03.440
We will protect you.

33:03.520 --> 33:04.520
Sang Zhi.

33:05.200 --> 33:06.520
- I'm sorry.
- One last thing.

33:08.600 --> 33:09.880
You should focus on your studies

33:10.360 --> 33:12.000
at your age.

33:13.920 --> 33:16.520
Do not loiter in shady areas.

33:25.040 --> 33:26.840
The topic for today's written exam

33:26.920 --> 33:28.280
is "My Dream."

33:28.880 --> 33:30.520
Pass the exam papers to the back.

33:35.200 --> 33:36.920
ESSAY TOPIC: MY DREAM

34:03.280 --> 34:04.280
Sit here.

34:05.640 --> 34:06.520
Watch from here.

34:08.880 --> 34:09.760
Zhizhi.

34:14.639 --> 34:17.000
Zhizhi, we want to talk to you.

34:17.719 --> 34:18.600
Sit here.

34:22.320 --> 34:23.639
Be careful.

34:24.719 --> 34:25.560
Come forward.

34:28.040 --> 34:29.360
Here, Zhizhi.

34:30.159 --> 34:31.840
These are the results of your final exams.

34:32.400 --> 34:33.800
Take a look.

34:37.080 --> 34:40.080
XURI MIDDLE-HIGH SCHOOL
GRADE 11 FIRST-TERM FINAL EXAM RESULTS

34:43.600 --> 34:44.440
PHYSICS, 66 POINTS

34:44.520 --> 34:46.040
I passed physics!

34:48.159 --> 34:49.679
Do you think you did well?

34:50.239 --> 34:51.280
No.

34:51.360 --> 34:52.960
I don't like physics,

34:53.040 --> 34:55.239
so I didn't pay attention during class.

34:55.320 --> 34:58.040
I skimmed through the textbook
before the exam

34:58.120 --> 34:59.720
and I actually passed.

34:59.800 --> 35:00.840
Are you proud of it?

35:00.920 --> 35:01.960
No.

35:04.360 --> 35:05.600
Zhizhi,

35:05.680 --> 35:07.480
you study for yourself

35:08.120 --> 35:09.320
and your future,

35:09.400 --> 35:10.480
not for us.

35:11.040 --> 35:12.760
Have you thought about what you want to do

35:12.840 --> 35:14.560
in the future?

35:14.640 --> 35:15.920
What is your dream?

35:17.720 --> 35:20.080
This was an essay topic during the exams.

35:20.160 --> 35:21.040
What did you write?

35:22.040 --> 35:24.280
I wrote that my dream is

35:26.000 --> 35:27.840
peace and love.

35:29.040 --> 35:31.280
For everyone to care for each other.

35:33.080 --> 35:34.320
Look, Zhizhi.

35:34.400 --> 35:37.040
What your mom and I are talking about

35:37.120 --> 35:39.120
is what kind of career

35:39.200 --> 35:40.720
you want for yourself.

35:41.240 --> 35:42.440
I want to draw.

35:42.520 --> 35:44.360
Can I draw for a living?

35:44.440 --> 35:45.360
Is that all?

35:48.240 --> 35:52.040
Either way, physics will not play a part

35:52.120 --> 35:53.600
in my life.

35:55.560 --> 35:56.480
I think.

35:58.360 --> 35:59.280
Zhizhi.

35:59.800 --> 36:03.120
Before you have figured out
what you want to do with your life,

36:03.200 --> 36:05.280
you should get some help with physics.

36:05.920 --> 36:07.920
Your class teacher and I talked and agreed

36:08.000 --> 36:09.360
that you're weak in some subjects.

36:09.440 --> 36:11.400
We'll hire a tutor during winter break

36:12.080 --> 36:13.920
to help you with physics.

36:15.400 --> 36:16.560
No use seeking help.

36:16.640 --> 36:17.840
Ask yourself honestly.

36:17.920 --> 36:19.520
Do you need help with physics?

36:31.160 --> 36:33.480
So you're the tutor that Dad hired?

36:33.560 --> 36:34.600
Yes.

36:35.280 --> 36:36.320
Listen now.

36:36.400 --> 36:38.720
I scored over 270 points
in the science portion of the NCEE.

36:38.800 --> 36:40.160
Don't underestimate me.

36:40.240 --> 36:41.120
Snobbish, aren't you?

36:41.200 --> 36:42.160
Rightfully so.

36:44.760 --> 36:46.680
Hey, come on.

36:46.760 --> 36:48.280
You scored 66 points.

36:48.360 --> 36:49.720
How dare you criticize me?

36:49.800 --> 36:51.400
Score 666 and we can talk.

36:53.880 --> 36:55.520
I don't want you to be my tutor.

36:55.600 --> 36:56.480
Bye.

36:56.560 --> 36:57.640
Sit down.

36:58.160 --> 36:59.080
Pay attention.

37:00.200 --> 37:01.040
Let me see.

37:03.400 --> 37:04.240
Okay.

37:04.320 --> 37:06.520
Kepler's laws of planetary motion.

37:08.520 --> 37:09.440
Listen to me.

37:09.520 --> 37:10.960
Do you know the three laws?

37:11.040 --> 37:12.280
No? Okay.

37:13.440 --> 37:15.840
This is the formula of gravity.

37:15.920 --> 37:17.440
What is F? F is the force of gravity.

37:17.520 --> 37:20.360
G is the gravitational constant.

37:20.440 --> 37:21.800
M is the mass.

37:21.880 --> 37:23.600
You have a capital M and a lowercase m.

37:23.680 --> 37:24.720
Both are masses.

37:25.600 --> 37:28.320
What is R?
R is the distance between two bodies.

37:28.400 --> 37:30.440
- Next question.
- Wait. What is this R?

37:30.520 --> 37:32.520
All Rs stand for distance. Moving on.

37:32.600 --> 37:34.160
Wait. Don't move on just yet.

37:34.240 --> 37:36.120
F is…

37:36.200 --> 37:37.440
This is the third time now!

37:37.520 --> 37:40.560
- F is the force of gravity.
- Wait! F and G are different.

37:40.640 --> 37:41.960
Both Ms are Masses.

37:42.040 --> 37:44.240
- What is R squared?
- This R is distance!

37:44.320 --> 37:46.400
You didn't explain anything!

37:46.480 --> 37:48.520
You're too dumb.

37:48.600 --> 37:49.720
It's not my fault.

37:50.480 --> 37:51.720
Sang Yan, you'll pay for this!

37:51.800 --> 37:52.760
You're done for!

37:52.840 --> 37:54.080
- Die!
- You don't get anything.

37:54.160 --> 37:55.320
Die, Sang Yan!

37:56.000 --> 37:57.200
Mom!

37:58.080 --> 37:59.320
Are you scared now?

37:59.400 --> 38:00.520
Go back and study!

38:17.280 --> 38:18.160
She's too dumb.

38:18.240 --> 38:19.640
He's impatient.

38:19.720 --> 38:21.160
- Get someone else.
- Get someone else.

38:21.240 --> 38:23.000
Okay, we'll find another tutor.

38:23.080 --> 38:24.720
I don't want you to bicker all day long

38:24.800 --> 38:26.520
and ruin my wife's mood.

38:27.560 --> 38:28.720
I didn't say anything.

38:29.360 --> 38:30.880
It's mainly because your dad

38:30.960 --> 38:31.920
can't put up with this.

38:32.680 --> 38:34.960
Also, can she be tutored

38:35.040 --> 38:36.920
in her own room

38:37.000 --> 38:38.640
instead of in my room?

38:38.720 --> 38:40.280
- No.
- Why not?

38:40.360 --> 38:41.840
I'm not the one being tutored.

38:41.920 --> 38:44.600
I don't want a stranger
going into my room.

38:44.680 --> 38:46.400
I don't want a stranger

38:46.480 --> 38:48.000
going into my room either!

38:48.080 --> 38:49.840
Enough. Can you two stop arguing?

38:49.920 --> 38:51.040
Sang Yan.

38:51.120 --> 38:54.000
Do you think your dad and I

38:54.080 --> 38:55.960
will let a stranger
into your sister's room?

38:56.040 --> 38:57.880
That's right. I'll be worried too.

38:57.960 --> 38:59.920
Yes, I'll be scared too.

39:04.120 --> 39:04.960
I see.

39:05.040 --> 39:06.000
I'm just human CCTV.

39:06.680 --> 39:07.560
I get it.

39:07.640 --> 39:08.920
Then be good CCTV.

39:20.720 --> 39:21.640
Zhizhi.

39:27.280 --> 39:28.280
I thought you were asleep.

39:28.360 --> 39:29.480
Mom, I drew Sang Yan.

39:29.560 --> 39:31.360
MY NAME IS SANG YAN

39:31.920 --> 39:33.440
You gave him a pair of glasses.

39:35.680 --> 39:36.520
Smell this.

39:37.000 --> 39:38.040
Isn't it fragrant?

39:38.920 --> 39:40.880
I already found a tutor for you.

39:42.600 --> 39:44.080
At 10 a.m. tomorrow,

39:44.160 --> 39:45.360
he will come here to tutor you.

39:45.440 --> 39:47.800
Sleep soon and wake up early.

39:50.760 --> 39:52.240
Drink this oat milk.

39:52.320 --> 39:53.200
Good night.

39:53.280 --> 39:54.280
Sleep soon.

40:05.920 --> 40:07.640
She found another tutor.

40:08.160 --> 40:10.680
She found someone so quickly!

40:11.200 --> 40:12.640
I don't want a tutor!

40:12.720 --> 40:14.160
I don't want lessons!

40:19.600 --> 40:20.600
Silly dog!

40:27.920 --> 40:30.920
Maybe I should sneak out tomorrow morning.

40:32.080 --> 40:33.000
That way,

40:33.080 --> 40:34.720
the tutor will know I'm difficult

40:34.800 --> 40:36.120
and will quit on the spot.

41:21.760 --> 41:23.960
Xiaoduan, this is the 3D model document.

41:24.040 --> 41:25.720
Crosscheck and return it
by the end of the day.

41:25.800 --> 41:26.640
Okay.

41:33.440 --> 41:34.600
Li Xun.

41:35.800 --> 41:37.040
Jiaxu.

41:37.120 --> 41:39.080
Your optimization is perfect.

41:39.160 --> 41:40.040
Thank you.

41:40.720 --> 41:41.680
Well done.

41:41.760 --> 41:42.640
It's my job.

41:43.360 --> 41:44.200
By the way,

41:44.920 --> 41:46.040
I remember from your resume

41:46.120 --> 41:47.120
that you're from Yihe.

41:47.720 --> 41:48.560
Yes.

41:48.640 --> 41:49.880
I'm also from Yihe.

41:50.520 --> 41:51.960
- Really?
- What was your high school?

41:52.040 --> 41:53.120
I went to No. 2 High School.

41:53.200 --> 41:54.520
I went to Yihe No. 3 High School.

41:54.600 --> 41:55.680
I knew it.

41:55.760 --> 41:58.000
I would have heard

41:58.080 --> 41:59.400
of such a handsome junior.

42:00.680 --> 42:02.840
I know you're graduating soon.

42:02.920 --> 42:05.240
Will you return to Yihe?

42:08.640 --> 42:10.040
I'm still undecided.

42:10.120 --> 42:11.720
- Still undecided?
- Yes.

42:11.800 --> 42:14.400
Listen, this decision
will determine your career.

42:14.920 --> 42:16.760
Make sure to pick a city you like.

42:17.920 --> 42:19.040
I see.

42:19.120 --> 42:21.480
The company will assign me
to the headquarters in Yihe

42:21.560 --> 42:23.960
for the A Dream of Jianghu project
next year.

42:24.720 --> 42:26.360
If you're interested in returning to Yihe,

42:26.440 --> 42:27.680
we can work together.

42:28.360 --> 42:29.320
Thank you, Li Xun.

42:29.800 --> 42:30.800
I'll think about it.

42:30.880 --> 42:32.040
Do think about it.

42:32.120 --> 42:33.440
I'll let you work.

42:33.520 --> 42:35.080
- Okay.
- You have a bright future.

42:52.520 --> 42:53.440
What's up?

42:54.400 --> 42:57.440
Buddy, are you working late today?

42:57.520 --> 42:59.440
That depends on what you're about to say.

43:00.760 --> 43:02.320
Help me pick up your sister.
